        [
          "Classification",
          "Higher Education",
          "Blended Learning",
          "Performance on Course Exam",
          "Pass vs Warn",
          "424 students from Tohoku University",
          "1 Spring Semester Course and a 1 Fall Semester Course",
          "LMS logs",
          "[early_learning, study_in_time, catch_up, cramming, study_again, #videos_watched, #quizzes_taken, #audio_recordings, #listener_to_native_speaker, #listener_to_recorded_audio, #learning_sessions, duration_of_engagement]",
          "Every Week (Total 7 Periods)",
          "Authors draw from SRL models to create 5 of the variables used. \n\nAuthors use SMOTE. Data is always Aggregated from moment 1 to moment 7.",
          "RF-Benchmark,\nRF-Prospective",
          "5-Fold Cross-Validation",
          "Period 1\n{F1-Score: 0.235 - RF-Prospective, Accuracy: 0.824 - RF-Prospective, AUC: 0.559 - RF-Prospective, Precision: 0.353 - RF-Prospective, Recall: 0.176 - RF-Prospective, Specificity: 0.941 - RF-Prospective}\n\nPeriod 2\n{F1-Score: 0.431 - RF-Benchmark, Accuracy: 0.864 - RF-Prospective, AUC: 0.654 - RF-Benchmark, Precision: 0.667 - RF-Prospective, Recall: 0.380 - RF-Benchmark, Specificity: 0.979 - RF-Prospective}\n\nPeriod 3\n{F1-Score: 0.437 - RF-Benchmark, Accuracy: 0.860 - RF-Prospective, AUC: 0.670 - RF-Benchmark, Precision: 0.714 - RF-Prospective, Recall: 0.420 - RF-Benchmark, Specificity: 0.989 - RF-Prospective}\n\nPeriod 4\n{F1-Score: 0.476 - RF-Benchmark, Accuracy: 0.846 - RF-Prospective, AUC: 0.692 - RF-Benchmark, Precision: 0.500 - RF-Prospective, Recall: 0.480 - RF-Benchmark, Specificity: 0.920 - RF-Prospective}\n\nPeriod 5\n{F1-Score: 0.542 - RF-Prospective, Accuracy: 0.878 - RF-Prospective, AUC: 0.722 - RF-Benchmark, Precision: 0.640 - RF-Prospective, Recall: 0.520 - RF-Benchmark, Specificity: 0.952 - RF-Prospective}\n\nPeriod 6\n{F1-Score: 0.518 - RF-Benchmark, Accuracy: 0.882 - RF-Prospective, AUC: 0.714 - RF-Benchmark, Precision: 0750 - RF-Prospective, Recall: 0.500 - RF-Benchmark, Specificity: 0.979 - RF-Prospective}\n\nPeriod 7\n{F1-Score: 0.741 - RF-Prospective, Accuracy: 0.878 - RF-Prospective, AUC: 0.730 - RF-Benchmark, Precision: 0.706 - RF-Prospective, Recall: 0.540 - RF-Benchmark, F1-Score: 0.973 - RF-Prospective}",
          "Authors do 2 different works:\n\n1 - A Benchmark study which, across different periods does a holdout separation using the entire sample. \n\n2 - A prospective study which usus the 2018 version of the course as trainig and the 2019 as test data.\n\nThe comparison between RF-Benchmark and RF-Prospective shows that performance is better across the board. Authors use SHAP to understand the importance of the features and find study in time as being particularly relevant.",
          "- Small sample size\n\n- Does not consider other contexts - too course specific\n\n- Only uses RF\n\n- Does not consider additional data sources"
        ]
